1. Install py3status (package manager)
2. Clone this repository
3. Change your i3bar to use py3status in your i3 config:
	status_command py3status --include PY3STATUS_DIR
	where PY3STATUS_DIR is *this* directory
4. Add your chosen modules to i3status.conf file (normally in /etc/i3status.conf) 
	e.g.: order += "article50"
